      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1812-1846",
      "markText": "十年之前，我们是朋友，还可以问候；十年之后，我们是对手，只能够决斗。",
      "totalCount": 645,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1812&rangeEnd=1846",
