    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_13_3787-3831",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3787-3831",
      "markText": "夜深了还不想睡，你还在想着他吗？你这样痴情到底累不累？你不如死心塌地跟着我们曹操大人得了",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3787&rangeEnd=3831",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3787&rangeEnd=3831"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_6_2725-2790",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2725-2790",
      "markText": "第一，今后再有犯绑架罪的，一律不允许拿钱赎人；第二，今后再有犯绑架罪的，一律不允许考虑人质的安全，以惩治犯罪、消灭罪犯为第一要务。",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2725&rangeEnd=2790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2725&rangeEnd=2790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_6_8627-8674",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8627-8674",
      "markText": "如果一个社会中，连真正的人才都要通过歪门邪道，才能得到社会的认可，那么这个社会肯定是出问题了。",
      "totalCount": 533,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8627&rangeEnd=8674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8627&rangeEnd=8674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_12_8216-8247",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "8216-8247",
      "markText": "已有的事，后必再有；已行的事，后必再行。日光之下，并无新事。”",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=8216&rangeEnd=8247",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=8216&rangeEnd=8247"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_13_13440-13458",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "13440-13458",
      "markText": "世界上没有垃圾，只有放错地方的资源。",
      "totalCount": 493,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13440&rangeEnd=13458",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13440&rangeEnd=13458"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_4_3523-3558",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3523-3558",
      "markText": "曹操本身没有问题，问题在于曹操的评价者——我们。我们究竟出了什么问题？",
      "totalCount": 490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3523&rangeEnd=3558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3523&rangeEnd=3558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_4_5973-6054",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5973-6054",
      "markText": "就这样，整个东汉王朝不是外戚压倒宦官，就是宦官推翻外戚，外戚和宦官互相夺权、轮流执政。皇帝呢，只好穿着龙袍跑龙套，被晾在一边看热闹。这几乎成了东汉政治的基本模式。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021703&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5973&rangeEnd=6054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ca132690813ab6efag0136b7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5973&rangeEnd=6054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021703_11_2025-2076",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2025-2076",
      "markText": "一个人权势煊赫之际，对他摇一次头；一个人声名狼藉之时，为他叹一口气。两者都需要纯粹的良心，莫大的勇气。",
